arts.ttl: Zhegrova's goal gives Lille a 1-0 win against Rennes in French league
arts.sum: Edon Zhegrova continued his fine form with the only goal as fourth-place Lille beat Rennes 1-0 in the French league on Sunday to stay one point behind Marseille in third. The 25-year-old Zhegrova made similar attacking runs when Lille drew 1-1 with Juventus in the Champions League three weeks ago, providing a superb assist for David’s goal.

arts.ttl: Angel Gomes: How Man Utd and Amorim should react to Spurs hijack
arts.sum: Angel Gomes played for Man Utd from youth level all the way up to the first team, featuring 10 times for the Red Devils, including five Premier League appearances. It must certainly be tempting for Man Utd to bring Angel Gomes back to the club from Lille .
